OL,5, A Post Office scandal victim has called
OL,6, for a top lawyer to be removed from    
OL,7, administering Horizon redress schemes. 
OL,9,FFormer sub-postmaster Lee Castleton    
OL,10,Fsaid Rodric Williams was "conflicted". 
OL,12,FMr Williams was a litigation lawyer at 
OL,13,Fthe Post Office while it was           
OL,14,Fprosecuting sub-postmasters.           
OL,16,FSeparately, it emerged at an ongoing   
OL,17,Finquiry that Mr Williams had described 
OL,18,Fa campaigner who tried to draw         
OL,19,Fattention to faults in Horizon software
OL,20,Fin 2015 as a "bluffer".                
